Raigodd moharaxttrantolo ek namnecho itihasik kil'lo ani xivchhtropotin ghoddoil'lea hindvi svorajeachi rajdhani. Raigodd jilheant to mohaddoche ut'torek 25 kimi. Ontracher ani zonjireache udentek 65 kimi. Ontracher soheadri dongor 5.125 chovo. Kimi. Cher asa. Tachi unchai 846 mi. Asun, sorbhomvotonni sandoxi, chhotri nizamopur, vagheri vaddi, pachadd oxa kheddeancho punzulo dista. Rairi hem dongul'lechem pornem namv. Jibradhy osoi tacho ul'lekh kortat. Ixanyekodde linganna, udentekodde tornna, dokxinnekodde kangora, chambharogodd, sonarogodd, vaivyekodde tollegodd, ut'terokodde ghosallogodd he godd raigodd kil'leabhomvotonni rakhnnodar koxe ube rauleat. Techkhatir xivaji moharazan thoim rajdhanichi sthapna keli.

==Dantkotha==

Xivaji – Sombhaji hanchea kallant ingroz, ddoch, purtugez hea vokilani. Hea kileak bhett divn tachem vornnon boroun dourolam. 12 vea xenkddeant rairi hem moratthi pallegaranchem nivassthan aslem. 14 vea xenkddeant hea pallegaramni vizoinogorachem manddliktv apnnailem. I. So. 1436 to dusro ol'laudin bohmonixahan raigodd aplea tabeant ghetlo. I.So. 1479 to ohmodonogorachea nizamoxahan rairi aplea tabeant ghetli. Istombol ho tacho kil'ledar dili. Fuddem 1621 to molik zomrun ho houlodar zalo. Magir porot ho kil'lo nizamoxahint gelo. Moglani nizamoxahi noxtt keleauporant adiloxahan zal'le koblatipromann rairi adiloxahikodde aili. Adiloxahint 1636 te 1644 chea odmasak zonjireachea sidhdi ghoranneantolo ibrahim'-soiyod kobbori ani xekh oli hankam hovalodaricho hokk dilo. Chondroravo more hachekodde rairi adiloxahachea votin geli. Xivaji moharazan zaulli jikun 1656 chea sumarak chondroravo moreakoddole soglle kil'le kabiz kelo. 15 epril te 14 me 1656 chea odmasak rairi xivajichea hatant aili. Ten'na xivajin rairichem raigodd namv dourolem ani tin char vorsambhitor thoim lhan vhodd tinxem vastu bandleo. 1662 vorsa xivajin rajdhanikhatir raigoddachi nivdd keli ani 1674 to to chhotropoti sombhajichea tabeant aslo. Fuddem moglamni to ghetlo. 1689 to porot morattheamni ghetlo. 1735 to kil'lo ut'tor pexvaint rajki-i bondeanchi bondkhonn zal'li. Nana foddnnis ani dusro bajiravo hannem poddttea kallant tacho alaxiro ghetlo. Morattheancho porabhou korun brittix loxkori odhikari kornol prothran 10 me 1818 to raigodd jikun ghetlo. Teachvellar tofanchea mareant zaito imaroti moddleo. Te uprant xivzointi utsovanimotan 1897 to lokmany ttillok smritini lokzagritayekolagun hea itihasik vastukodden porot lokx dilem, atam tem poryottokanchem ek prekxonni-i stholl zalam. Nogarokhana, monore, buruz, deullam oxo kaim vostu noxtt zal'leo asun legit, te vastuche bhouyotechi kolpona yeta. Kil'leak hirkonni, ttokmok, bhovani ani xrigonde oxim char tonkam asun, ttokmok tonk ani hirkonnivixim zaiteo kotha prosid'd asat.

Chor darakheriz kil'leak ekuch vhoddlem dar asa. Sogllea vottamni katoll ani kodden tottbondi asa. Nannedar hem raigoddachem survatichem provexodar asun, tacho bhitrole votten mohadar lagta. Thoim 22 mittor unchayeche don buruz asat. Monoreache ostontek ekvis sopnnam choddun geleauporant balekil'leachem dar lagta. Tachem kxetrofoll 300 x 150 mittor asun, sorbhomvotonni tottbondi asa. Bhitroleutten porne imaroticheo don volli lagtat. Ujveutten ranneanche sat mhal asun daveutten nokrancheo kuddi asat. Balekil'leache modim simhasanacho chouthoro asun to susthitint asa. Simhasona mukhar fovare asun, tache mukhar udentek 16 mittor unchayecho bhouy nogarokhano ani balekil'leachem mukhel provexodar asa. Hangach xivaji moharazacho dorbar bhortalo. Hea sobhaghoracho avazache nodren vichar kel'lo asa. Karonn nagrokhaneamukhar axil'le vyoktik simhasonalagim uloil'lem spoxtt aikunk yeta. Tachea mukhar xivajicho vaddo ani tea bhomvtonni karealoyin imaroti asat.

Nagrokhaneache udentek kuxaurt namvachem tollem asun, leginch xrigonde tonk asa. Toxench xivajichea oxtt prodhananche vadde asat. Tachea mukhar darukhaneachem kotthra 25 x 6 mi. Asa. Balekil'leachem vaivyek pilkhaneachi jirnnoxirnn vastu, tache ut'terok goddauylea bazaropetthecho ovxex, donuy vottentolim mellun sumar 44 dukanam asat. Donoi rankent forsobondi asun bara mi. Rund rosto asa. Thoinchean ixanyechea prakarant hemaddoponti pod'dotin bandil'lem zogdixrvor mohadevachem devull asun, tachea provexodarakodde marutichi sobit paxanni murti asa. Deullabhomvotonni nriteangonancheo mititithi ani xoke hacho ul'lekh asa. Deullachea udent daramukhar xivchhtropotinchi somadhi ani ghumttakriti yadistik asun, tachea mukhar imani vadea sunneachem-i yadstik asa. Te bhair foramodaroxah hea muslin sadhuchi kobor, hot'ti tollem, gongasagor tollem heoi vastu asat.

